testcase.name: prepend default prefix to reserve word funciton
prepend default prefix to reserve word funciton should be idempotent
should not prepend default prefix to non reserve word chet
unprepend should not work on non reserve words
be able to add arrays to reserve words list
be able to add a string to reserve words list
get prefix should return "reserve_" default prefix
set prefix "new_prefix_" and prefix "function" should return "new_prefix_function"
